creator: racemap.com
descriptionHtml:
Racemap broadcasts your sports event real-time to the Internet and smartphones. For spectators, athletes and event organizers.
Easy GPS Tracking for sports events with your smartphone - family, friends and fans keep track to your race from everywhere and the live stream shows an overview over the competition.
After the sports event you can replay the race.
descriptionShort: Live Tracking of Sports Events, providing interactive Map for Spectators
